'''Champagne''' was an [[Alcohol/Legends|alcoholic]] beverage. [[Xizor/Legends|Xizor]] enjoyed [[green champagne]]. [[Daruvvian champagne]] was another type. [[Gavin Darklighter]] and [[Sera Faleur Darklighter|Sera Faleur]] had a [[champagne fountain]] at their wedding.

